{"tid":1400470,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角「威威小食」送咗兩支水畀我哋","createTime":"2019-08-03T13:02:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T23:38:16.000Z","uid":166054,"like":470,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d77bbcd613b8fe6a55a8001956771fe9e02a962b","tid":1400470,"uid":166054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:02:19.000Z","msg":"夜晚發夢夢見自己去咗旺角<br />\n見8成舖都閂咗，得少數有開（多數係食店）<br />\n咁我見行街shopping嘅人真係好少，佢哋舖租又貴，有啲歉疚，就諗住幫襯下佢哋等佢哋唔好咁悶咁愁啦<br />\n求其發夢去咗家樂坊對面嘅呢間「威威小食」買咗串辣魚蛋<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCcqDwn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCcqDwn.png&h=34f2e3cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畀完錢我就同老闆展開咗以下呢段對話（我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，老闆：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：唔好意思呀真係（唔想講到咁白話阻住佢做生意咁老土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：（望住我Load咗陣）哦，唔緊要啦，明嘅，有冇上前線呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我........ er...... 咩線都有啲啦😅（戴頭盔sor)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哦，喂，（遞兩支Bonaqua水畀我，如下圖），拎上去畀前線呀，少少意思啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bm8pT4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbm8pT4b.png&h=b1a44f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：噢！好多謝你！<br />\n<br />\n雖然兩支水唔係咩貴重嘢，不過老細對我哋嘅心意真係收到晒呀<br />\n大家發夢嗰陣不如多啲幫襯「威威小食」啦！就算夢醒都幫襯多啲！<br />\n<br />\nPS: 佢粒辣魚蛋夠辣，辣得好過癮；魚蛋又有咬口，唔削，幾好𡁻，高汁！10蚊8粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a42e8a647735c439739fcacdeca59495c2a695","tid":1400470,"uid":16664,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:04:03.000Z","msg":"光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0728ca7e5a10bfbd653d56adde5d80b74eaaeee8","tid":1400470,"uid":166054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:12:30.000Z","msg":"支持小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a45a4e0211673b3173ced345db690fdf8632d80","tid":1400470,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:14:19.000Z","msg":"下次經過會食"},{"pid":"cf6a88fe421dcfb917fb45d8d37b7da64a8a78d3","tid":1400470,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:15:30.000Z","msg":"想幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10325b19d73c19ab58548b3825c022ffc0d14e1a","tid":1400470,"uid":188310,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:17:08.000Z","msg":"你咁威威，就去幫襯你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189877dc183a4e139a341d7fa867e6eebaf2a47e","tid":1400470,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5feb47c74cf23886cc309a955a8b707701e9117","tid":1400470,"uid":18110,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:19:31.000Z","msg":"佢啲雞蛋仔好食，chef lemon 都收皮"},{"pid":"2ad45bc6a79aa934bf7acacbaae8924973338a2d","tid":1400470,"uid":272565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"陳皮魚蛋？"},{"pid":"fd3480691c1a2658f87bb7f66e492194327a5ba6","tid":1400470,"uid":258381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a103cb72988b0f8092302a2c05cec884cb8f14d","tid":1400470,"uid":166054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ad45bc6a79aa934bf7acacbaae8924973338a2d","tid":1400470,"uid":272565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"reply